               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maftǝḥe śǝrāy “Undoing of Charms”: 5 protective prayers (fols.
                     1r-12v), incomplete (incipit is missing)
 II) Gǝrmā mogas, ʾAsmāt-prayer
                     for acquiring charisma (fols. 15r-45r), incomplete (cp. EMML nos. 1380,
                     3508)
 III) Directives for reading the sacred books (?) (fols.
                     47r-51v)
 IV) Malkǝʾa Fānuʾel “Image of Phanuʾel” (fols. 55r-83v),
                     incomplete (the final fols. are missing) (ChRep p. 202, no. 166)
 
                     Additio 1.</summary>

               </msContents>
